Class Summary
EMail The email message is similar to the format and purpose of the News message, however, it is intended for private use between two parties.

Quote The Quote message is used as the response to a Quote Request or a Quote Response message in both indicative, tradeable, and restricted tradeable quoting markets.

QuoteRequestReject not in use currently
